    "output": "def max_thermometer_reading(l):\n    '''This function computes the maximum thermometer reading given as a list of strings'''\n    order = {'F': 0, 'C': 1}\n    max_val = float('-inf')\n    for reading in l:\n        num, unit = reading[:-1], reading[-1]\n        if order[unit] > order[max_val[-1]]:\n            max_val = reading\n        elif order[unit] == order[max_val[-1]]:\n            if float(max_val[:-1]) < float(num):\n                max_val = reading\n    return max_val",
