    "output": "public static boolean checkAnagrams(String s1, String s2) { \n    int[] count1 = new int[256]; \n    int[] count2 = new int[256]; \n  \n    // edge cases\n    if (s1.length() != s2.length()) \n        return false; \n\n    for (int i = 0; i < s1.length(); i++) { \n        count1[s1.charAt(i)]++; \n        count2[s2.charAt(i)]++; \n    } \n  \n    for (int i = 0; i < 256; i++) \n        if (count1[i] != count2[i]) \n            return false; \n  \n    return true; \n}",
