    "instruction": "Design an algorithm to find all the elements that occur an odd number of times in an array.",
    "input": "arr[] = {5, 4, 2, 5, 2, 1, 4, 5}",
    "output": "function findOddOccurrences(arr) { \n    let result = []; \n  \n    // Iterate over each element \n    for (let i = 0; i < arr.length; i++) { \n  \n        // Initialize count \n        let count = 0; \n  \n        // Iterate over the rest of the elements \n        for (let j = 0; j < arr.length; j++) { \n            // If the current element is equal to other, \n            // increment the count \n            if (arr[i] == arr[j]) { \n                count++; \n            } \n        } \n  \n        // If the count is odd, add the element to the result \n        if (count % 2 != 0) { \n            result.push(arr[i]); \n        } \n    } \n  \n    return result; \n}",
    "category": "code_instruction"
