    "instruction": "Create a function to find the shortest route from one point to another in a given matrix.",
    "input": "",
    "output": "def find_shortest_route(matrix, start, end):\n    queue = collections.deque([[start]])\n    visited = set()\n\n    while queue:\n        path = queue.popleft()\n        node = path[-1]\n\n        if node == end: \n            return path\n\n        for next_node in matrix[node]:\n            if next_node not in visited:\n                queue.append(path + [next_node])\n                visited.add(next_node)\n\n    return []",
    "category": "code_instruction"
