    "output": "def merge_sort(arr):\n\tif len(arr) > 1:\n\t\tmid = len(arr) // 2\n\t\tleft = arr[:mid]\n\t\tright = arr[mid:]\n\n\t\tmerge_sort(left)\n\t\tmerge_sort(right)\n\n\t\ti, j, k = 0, 0, 0\n\t\twhile i < len(left) and j < len(right):\n\t\t\tif left[i] < right[j]:\n\t\t\t\tarr[k] = left[i]\n\t\t\t\ti += 1\n\t\t\telse:\n\t\t\t\tarr[k] = right[j]\n\t\t\t\tj += 1\n\t\t\tk += 1\n\n\t\twhile i < len(left):\n\t\t\tarr[k] = left[i]\n\t\t\ti += 1\n\t\t\tk += 1\n\n\t\twhile j < len(right):\n\t\t\tarr[k] = right[j]\n\t\t\tj += 1\n\t\t\tk += 1",
    "category": "code_instruction"
