    "instruction": "Create a genetic algorithm to optimize the given problem.",
    "input": "Problem: Given a set of protein sequences, find the optimal set of sequences with the highest probability of converging to a given structure.",
    "output": "def genetic_algorithm(population, target_sequence, mutation_rate, num_generations):\n    # Length of the target sequence\n    target_length = len(target_sequence)\n \n    # Create a dictionary to store the best sequence in each generation\n    best_sequences = {}\n \n    # Generate the initial pool of sequences\n    for i in range(population):\n        # Generate a random sequence\n        sequence = \"\".join(np.random.choice([\"A\", \"G\", \"C\", \"T\"], target_length))\n        # Calculate the fitness value of the sequence\n        fitness = calculate_fitness(sequence, target_sequence)\n        # Store the sequence and its fitness in the dictionary\n        best_sequences[sequence] = fitness\n \n    for generation in range(num_generations):\n        # Create a new population\n        new_population = []\n        for _ in range(population):\n            # Select two random sequences\n            parent_1, parent_2 = np.random.choice(list(best_sequences.keys()), 2)\n            # Create a child sequence by crossing over the two parents\n            child = crossover(parent_1, parent_2, target_length)\n            # Add random mutations\n            child = mutate(child, mutation_rate)\n            # Calculate the fitness value of the child\n            fitness = calculate_fitness(child, target_sequence)\n            # Store the child sequence and its fitness in the dictionary\n            best_sequences[child] = fitness\n            # Add the child to the new population\n            new_population.append(child)\n \n        # Select the best sequences from the new population\n        best_sequences = select_best(best_sequences, new_population, target_sequence)\n \n    # Return the best sequence of the last generation\n    return max(best_sequences, key=best_sequences.get)",
