    "output": "def find_pairs_summing_to(nums, target): \n    result = []\n    for i in range(len(nums) - 1):\n        for j in range(i + 1, len(nums)):\n            if nums[i] + nums[j] == target:\n                result.append([nums[i], nums[j]])\n    \n    return result \n\nprint(find_pairs_summing_to([1, 5, 7, -1, 5], 6)) # Output: [[5, 1], [-1, 7]]",
