    "input": "",
    "output": "def is_identical_tree(node1, node2):\n    \n    # If both trees are empty, return True\n    if node1 is None and node2 is None:\n        return True\n\n    # If one of them is empty, return False\n    if node1 is None or node2 is None:\n        return False\n\n    # If both nodes have same value and left and right subtree are also identical\n    return (node1.data == node2.data and\n            is_identical_tree(node1.left, node2.left) and is_identical_tree(node1.right, node2.right))\n\nresult = is_identical_tree(node1, node2)\nprint(result)",
