    "output": "# Create a queue\nqueue = []\n\n# Enqueue the root node\nqueue.append(root)\n\n# Initialize an empty list to store the result\nresult = []\n\n# Loop until there are items in the queue\nwhile len(queue) > 0:\n  # Dequeue the front node\n  front = queue.pop(0)\n  \n  # Append the data of the dequeued node in the result list\n  result.append(front.val)\n\n  # Enqueue the left and right children of the dequeued node \n  if front.left:\n    queue.append(front.left)\n  if front.right:\n    queue.append(front.right)",
