    "input": "arr = [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6], d = 2",
    "output": "\"\"\"\nImplementing an algorithm to do in-place rotation of an array\n\"\"\"\ndef rotate_array(arr, d):\n    n = len(arr)\n    d = d % n\n    reverse(arr, 0, d-1)\n    reverse(arr, d, n-1)\n    reverse(arr, 0, n-1)\n\ndef reverse(arr, start, end):\n    while(start < end):\n        arr[start], arr[end] = arr[end], arr[start]\n        start += 1\n        end -= 1\n\nif __name__ == '__main__':\n    arr = [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6]\n    d = 2\n    rotate_array(arr, d)\n    print(arr)",
