    "output": "def search_for_target(nums, target)\n left = 0\n right = nums.length - 1\n\n while left <= right\n mid = (left + right) / 2\n\n if nums[mid] == target\n return mid\n\n if nums[mid] > target\n right = mid - 1\n else\n left = mid + 1\n end\n end\n\n return -1\nend\n\nputs search_for_target([1, 2, 3, 4, 5], 3)",
