    "input": "arr = [3, 5, 2, 6, 4, 7]",
    "output": "def sort_array(arr): \n    for i in range(len(arr)): \n        smallest = arr[i] \n        smallest_index = i \n        for j in range(i+1, len(arr)): \n            if arr[j] < smallest: \n                smallest = arr[j] \n                smallest_index = j \n        arr[i], arr[smallest_index] = smallest, arr[i] \n    return arr \n\narr = [3, 5, 2, 6, 4, 7]\nprint(sort_array(arr)) # [2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7]",
