    "instruction": "Write an algorithm which sorts an array of numbers in O(n logn) time.",
    "input": "[7,3,2,5,9,8,6]",
    "output": "def sort(array):\n if len(array) == 0:\n return array\n\n left = []\n right = []\n pivot = array[0]\n\n for num in array[1:]:\n if num <= pivot:\n left.append(num)\n else:\n right.append(num)\n\n left = sort(left)\n right = sort(right)\n\n return left + [pivot] + right\n\narr = [7,3,2,5,9,8,6]\nsortedArray = sort(arr)\nprint(sortedArray)\n\n# Output: [2, 3, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9]",
    "category": "code_instruction"
