    "input": "[9, 4, 2, 5, 7, 1, 6, 8]",
    "output": "public static int longestIncreasingSequence(int[] arr) {\n    int len = arr.length;\n    int[] lis = new int[len];\n\n    lis[0] = 1;\n    int max_length = 1;\n\n    for (int i = 1; i < len; i++) {\n        lis[i] = 1;\n        for (int j = 0; j < i; j++) {\n            if (arr[j] < arr[i] && lis[i] < lis[j] + 1) {\n                lis[i] = lis[j] + 1;\n                max_length = Math.max(max_length, lis[i]);\n            }\n        }\n    }\n\n    return max_length;\n}",
