    "output": "def max_depth(node): \n    if node is None: \n        return 0 ;  \n  \n    else : \n  \n        # Compute the depth of each subtree \n        ldepth = max_depth(node.left) \n        rdepth = max_depth(node.right) \n  \n        # Return the depth of the subtree that has a greater depth \n        if (ldepth > rdepth): \n            return ldepth+1\n        else: \n            return rdepth+1",
