    "instruction": "Design an algorithm that performs binary search on a sorted array.",
    "input": "<no input>",
    "output": "def binarySearch(arr, target): \n    low = 0\n    high = len(arr) - 1\n\n    while low <= high: \n        mid = (low + high) // 2\n        if arr[mid] == target:\n            return mid \n        elif arr[mid] < target: \n            low = mid + 1\n        else: \n            high = mid - 1\n    \n    return -1",
    "category": "code_instruction"
