    "instruction": "Develop a class which can find the area of a triangle.",
    "input": "",
    "output": "class Triangle:\n    def __init__(self, side1, side2, side3):\n        self.side1 = side1\n        self.side2 = side2\n        self.side3 = side3\n    \n    def area(self):\n        a = self.side1\n        b = self.side2\n        c = self.side3\n        s = (a + b + c) / 2\n        return ( s * (s-a) * (s-b) * (s-c) ) ** 0.5",
    "category": "code_instruction"
