    "input": "sorted_list = [0, 2, 4, 6, 8, 10]",
    "output": "def search(sorted_list, element):\n    low = 0\n    high = len(sorted_list) - 1\n    while low <= high:\n        mid = (low + high) // 2\n        if sorted_list[mid] == element:\n            return mid\n        elif sorted_list[mid] < element:\n            low = mid + 1\n        else:\n            high = mid - 1\n    return -1",
