    "output": "def DDA(x1, y1, x2, y2):  \n    dx = x2 - x1 \n    dy = y2 - y1 \n  \n    length = abs(dx) if abs(dx) > abs(dy) else abs(dy) \n  \n    dx = dx / length \n    dy = dy / length \n  \n    x = x1 \n    y = y1 \n  \n    for i in range(length + 1): \n        print(int(x), int(y)) \n        x = x + dx \n        y = y + dy",
