    "instruction": "Output the array after executing the selection sort.",
    "input": "arr = [5, 2, 3, 6, 7, 4]",
    "output": "arr = [2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7]\n\ndef selectionSort(arr):\n    n = len(arr)\n    for i in range(n-1):\n        index_smallest = i\n        for j in range(i+1, n):\n            if arr[j] < arr[index_smallest]:\n                index_smallest = j\n        arr[i], arr[index_smallest] = arr[index_smallest], arr[i]\n    return arr",
