    "instruction": "Write a Python program to generate n-grams of the given text with a window size of 3.",
    "input": "The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog",
    "output": "from collections import Counter\n\n\ndef generate_ngrams(text, window_size):\n    text = text.lower().split(' ')\n    ngrams = []\n    for n in range(window_size, len(text)+1):\n        for i in range(len(text)-n+1):\n            ngrams.append(' '.join(text[i:i+n]))\n    return Counter(ngrams)\n\n\ntext = \"The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog\"\nwindow_size = 3\n\nngrams_count = generate_ngrams(text, window_size)\n\nprint('\\nNGRAMS COUNT:',ngrams_count)\n\n# Output\n# NGRAMS COUNT: Counter({'the quick brown': 3,\n#            'quick brown fox': 2,\n#            'over the lazy': 1,\n#            'brown fox jumps': 1,\n#            'fox jumps over': 1,\n#            'the lazy dog': 1,\n#            'jumps over the': 1,\n#            'quick brown fox jumps': 1})",
