    "output": "//ascending order sort\nvoid Sort(int arr[], int size)\n{\n for(int i=0; i<size-1; i++)\n  {\n  int min_index = i;\n  for(int j=i+1; j<size; j++)\n   {\n   if(arr[j] < arr[min_index])\n    {\n    min_index = j;\n    }\n   }\n  int temp = arr[min_index];\n  arr[min_index] = arr[i];\n  arr[i] = temp;\n  }\n}",
    "category": "code_instruction"
