    "instruction": "Create an algorithm to find the GCD of two numbers.",
    "input": "",
    "output": "def gcd(a, b): \n    # Everything divides 0  \n    if (a == 0 or b == 0): \n        return 0\n  \n    # base case \n    if (a == b): \n        return a \n  \n    # a is greater \n    if (a > b): \n        return gcd(a-b, b) \n      \n    return gcd(a, b-a)",
