    "instruction": "Create a function to implement a binary search of an integer in an already sorted list.",
    "input": "",
    "output": "def binary_search(li, x):\n    start_index = 0\n    end_index = len(li) - 1\n    while start_index <= end_index:\n        mid_index = (start_index + end_index) // 2\n        if li[mid_index] == x: \n            return mid_index\n        elif li[mid_index] < x:\n            start_index = mid_index + 1\n        else:\n            end_index = mid_index - 1 \n    return -1",
    "category": "code_instruction"
