    "instruction": "Formulate an optimization algorithm to minimize the cost of a travel route.",
    "input": "",
    "output": "def minimize_cost_route(stops, costs):\n    if len(stops) == 0:\n        return 0\n    dp = [0 for i in range(len(stops))]\n    for i in range(1, len(stops)):\n        min_cost = float('inf')\n        for j in range(i):\n            min_cost = min(min_cost, dp[j]+ costs[(stops[j],stops[i])])\n        dp[i] = min_cost   \n    return dp[-1]",
    "category": "code_instruction"
