    "instruction": "Create a program to optimize a function using the gradient descent algorithm",
    "input": "",
    "output": "def gradient_descent(func, alpha, x):\n    cur_x = x\n    precision = 0.000001\n    max_iter = 10000\n    count = 0\n    while True:\n        gradient = func.derivative(cur_x)\n        previous_x = cur_x\n        cur_x = cur_x - alpha * gradient\n        difference = abs(cur_x - previous_x)\n        if difference < precision or count > max_iter:\n            break\n        count += 1\n    return cur_x",
    "category": "code_instruction"
