    "instruction": "Create a program to determine which of the two input strings are anagrams of each other.",
    "input": "",
    "output": "def isAnagram(string1, string2):\n    if len(string1) != len(string2):\n        return False\n \n    freq = [0] * 26\n    for c in string1:\n        freq[ord(c) - ord('a')] += 1\n \n    for c in string2:\n        freq[ord(c) - ord('a')] -= 1\n \n    for i in range(26):\n        if freq[i] != 0:\n            return False\n \n    return True",
    "category": "code_instruction"
