    "output": "def matrix_multiply(m1, m2):\n    result = [[0, 0], [0, 0]]\n    for i in range(len(m1)):\n        for j in range(len(m2[0])):\n            for k in range(len(m2)):\n                result[i][j] += m1[i][k] * m2[k][j]\n    return result\n\nA = [[1, 2], [3, 4]]\nB = [[2, 0], [1, 2]]\n\nresult = matrix_multiply(A, B)\n\nprint(result)\n\n# Output: [[4, 4], [10, 8]]",
