    "input": "",
    "output": "public static void sortDesc(int[] arr) {\n    Arrays.sort(arr);\n    reverse(arr);\n}\n\npublic static void reverse(int[] arr) {\n    int left  = 0;\n    int right = arr.length - 1;\n\n    while (left < right) {\n        int temp = arr[left];\n        arr[left]  = arr[right];\n        arr[right] = temp;\n\n        left++;\n        right--;\n    }\n}",
    "category": "code_instruction"
