    "output": "// Function to delete an element \nvoid deleteAtIndex(int arr[], int n, int index) \n{ \n    // Shift all the elements after the  \n    // element at given index one place behind \n    for (int i = index; i < n - 1; i++) \n        arr[i] = arr[i + 1]; \n  \n    // Decrease size after removing element \n    n--; \n  \n    // Print the array after deleting \n    for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) \n        cout << arr[i] << \" \"; \n} \n  \n// Driver Code \nint main() \n{ \n    int arr[] = {5, 2, 8, 4, 9}; \n    int n = sizeof(arr) / sizeof(arr[0]); \n    int index = 2; \n  \n    deleteAtIndex(arr, n, index); \n  \n    return 0; \n}",
