    "input": "Table with five columns: \nCol1 : ID (Integer) \nCol2: Name (String) \nCol3: Age (Integer) \nCol4: Height (Float) \nCol5: Experience (Integer)\n\nSample data: \nID | Name | Age | Height | Experience\n---|------|-----|--------|------------\n 1 | John | 20  | 1.89   | 5\n 2 | Jane | 22  | 1.60   | 3\n 3 | Mike | 18  | 1.89   | 2",
