    "instruction": "Create a memory efficient algorithm to check for palindrome words.",
    "input": "",
    "output": "def is_palindrome(word):\n    n = len(word)\n\n# A single character is always a palindrome\n    if n == 1:\n        return True\n    \n# Iterate through the string while two indexes left and right simultaneously\n    left, right = 0, n-1\n    while right >= left:\n        if word[left] != word[right]:\n            return False\n        left += 1\n        right -= 1\n    return True",
    "category": "code_instruction"
