    "input": "arr = [1, 2, 3, 4], target = 4",
    "output": "def findSubArraySums(nums, target) {\n  let result = [];\n  let temp = [];\n  findSubArraySumsHelper(nums, target, 0, temp, result);\n  return result;\n}\n\nfunction findSubArraySumsHelper(nums, target, start, temp, result) {\n  if (target === 0) {\n    result.push([...temp]);\n    return;\n  }\n \n  for (let i = start; i < nums.length; i++) {\n    temp.push(nums[i]);\n    findSubArraySumsHelper(nums, target - nums[i], i + 1, temp, result);\n    temp.pop();\n  }\n}\n\nfindSubArraySums([1, 2, 3, 4], 4);\n/* Expected output:\n[\n  [1, 3],\n  [2, 2],\n  [4]\n]\n*/",
    "category": "code_instruction"
