    "output": "def checkSequence(array):\n    # Edge case, if length of given array is less than 9\n    if len(array) < 9:\n        return False\n      \n    # iterate through array and check if pattern occurs  \n    for i in range(len(array) - 8):\n        # if number at index is 1 and following 8 numbers are 123456789 \n        # pattern is present, then return True   \n        if array[i] == 1 and array[i + 1 : i + 9] == [2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9]:\n            return True\n    return False\n\nprint(checkSequence([2, 3, 6, 7, 8, 1, 4, 5, 9]))",
