    "instruction": "Generate a list of all possible combinations of a given set of numbers.",
    "input": "[1, 2, 3]",
    "output": "\"\"\"\nGenerate a list of all possible combinations of a given set of numbers\n\"\"\"\n\ndef generate_combinations(numbers):\n    result_list = []\n    for i in range(1, 2 ** len(numbers)): \n        subset = []\n        for j in range(len(numbers)): \n            if (i & (1 << j)) > 0: \n                subset.append(numbers[j]) \n        result_list.append(subset)\n        \n    return result_list\n\nif __name__ == '__main__':\n    numbers = [1, 2, 3]\n    print(generate_combinations(numbers))",
    "category": "code_instruction"
