    "output": "def largest_sum(nums):\n    largest = max(nums[0], nums[1])\n    second_largest = min(nums[0], nums[1])\n    for elem in nums[2:]:\n        if elem > largest:\n            second_largest = largest\n            largest = elem \n        elif elem > second_largest:\n            second_largest = elem\n    return largest + second_largest",
