    "output": "#include <iostream> \nusing namespace std; \n  \n//swapping the content\nvoid swap(int* a, int* b) \n{ \n    int t = *a; \n    *a = *b; \n    *b = t; \n} \n  \n// Bubble sort\nvoid bubbleSort(int arr[], int n) \n{ \n   for (int i = 0; i < n-1; i++)     \n       for (int j = 0; j < n-i-1; j++)  \n           if (arr[j] > arr[j+1]) \n              swap(&arr[j], &arr[j+1]); \n} \n  \n// Print an array \nvoid printArray(int arr[], int n) \n{ \n   for (int i=0; i < n; i++) \n       cout << arr[i] << \" \"; \n   cout << endl; \n} \n  \nint main() \n{ \n     int arr[] = {2,3,5,1,4};\n     int n = sizeof(arr)/sizeof(arr[0]); \n     \n     bubbleSort(arr, n); \n    \n     cout<<\"Sorted array: \\n\"; \n     printArray(arr, n); \n     return 0; \n}",
